f Tropical Medicine \"Pedro Kouri\"]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://instituciones.sld.cu/ipk/|title=Instituto de Medicina Tropical Pedro Kour\u00ed|work=sld.cu|accessdate=2015-09-27}}</ref>\n# Czech Republic: [http://www.szu.cz/ National Institute of Public Health]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.szu.cz|title=SZ\u00da|work=szu.cz|accessdate=2015-09-27}}</ref>\n# Denmark: [https://www.sdu.dk/en/sif National Institute of Public Health]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sdu.dk/da/sif |title=Statens Institut for Folkesundhed, SDU |publisher=sdu.dk |date= |accessdate=2020-03-24}}</ref>\n# Ecuador: [http://www.investigacionsalud.gob.ec/ National Institute of Public Health Research]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.inspi.gob.ec/ |accessdate=July 22, 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419182727/http://www.inspi.gob.ec/ |archivedate=April 19, 2014 }}</ref>\n# England: [[Public Health England]]\n# Estonia: [http://www.tai.ee/ National Institute for Health and Development]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tai.ee|title=TAI|author=OKIA|work=tai.ee|accessdate=2015-09-27}}</ref>\n# Ethiopia : [http://ephi.gov.et/ Ethiopian Public Health Institute] <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ehnri.gov.et|title=Coming Soon|work=ehnri.gov.et|accessdate=2015-09-27}}</ref>\n# Finland: [[National Institute for Health and Welfare (Finland)|National Institute for Health and Welfare (THL)]]<ref name=\"thl.fi\">{{cite web|url=https://thl.fi/en/web/thlfi-en|title=Finnish Institute for Health and Welfare|work=Terveyden ja hyvinvoinnin laitos|publisher=thl.fi|accessdate=2020-03-24}}</ref>\n# France: [http://www.invs.sante.fr/ French Institute for Public Health Surveillance (InVS)]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.invs.sante.fr|title=InVS / Accueil|author=INVS|work=sante.fr|accessdate=2015-09-27}}</ref>\n# Georgia: [http://www.ncdc.ge/ Georgia National Center for Disease Control and Public Health (NCDC)]\n# Germany: [[Robert Koch Institute]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Koch Institute|url=http:/